 OKUNYE NGOJESU.
 Kwakukhona ofakazi abane ngesikhathi sikaJesu ababhala izincwadi ngoJesu. Lezizincwadi (amavangeli) zahlanganiswa ndawonye eBhayibhelini.
 NGOKUKAMATHEWU.
 UMathewu wayengomunye wabafundi bakaJesu abayishumi nambili. Wahlangana nabo ngenkathi uJesu embiza esebenza endlini lapho kuthelwa khona intela eKapernawume. Abantu babemangele ukuthi uJesu ufuna ukubanbisana nabathelisi. UMathewu wafakaza ngezindaba eziningi ngalokhu akubhalile.
 NGOKUKAMARKU.
 UMarku wabhala ivangeli elincane (incwadi ekhuluma ngempilo kaJesu yonke esho ukuthi ("izindaba ezinhle"). Kwakunguye kuphela ingane ngenkathi uJesu esebenza kwaIsrayeli. UMarku wayehamba kakhulu noPetru. Kwenye yezincwadi zakhe uPetru umthatha njenge "ndodana yakhe." Ekugcineni uMarku wayesehamba noPawulu owayeyindoda eyadlulisa umbiko kaJesu eYurobhu.
 NGOKUKALUKA.
 ULuka wabhala ivangeli nanxa wayengekho siqu sakhe lapho. Wayengudokotela engumGreki, waze wakholwa kuJesu. Wayehamba kakhulu noPawulu. ULuka wayevakashela ofakazi yena uqobo ukuze athole yonke indaba ngoJesu. Waphinda wabhala ngolwazi Iwamakholwa okuqala kanye nokuthi isonto lokuqala lamaKristu lalimiswa kanjani. Yaba incwadi eBhayibhelini ebizwa ngokuthi "Izenzo".
 NGOKUKAJOHANE.
 UJohane wahlala ethembekile kuJesu ngisho esesiphambanweni. Ekugcineni kwevangeli lakhe wabhala ukuthi "UJesu wenza nezinye izinto eziningi. Ngibhale lezizinto ukuze ukholwe ukuthi uJesu unguMesiya owathenjiswa, ukuze ube nempilo egameni lakhe." Kubo bonke abalandeli bakaJesu, uJohane nguyena kuphela owaphila impilo ende. Ekugcineni uJohane wathola umbono kaJesu njengoba enjalo manje, iNdodana kaNkulunkulu enenkazimulo. Kwabhalwa encwadini yeSambulo.
 NAWE FUTHI!
 Indaba kaJesu ayikapheli. Eminyakeni yezinkulungwane iqhubekile ezimpilweni zabantu abaningi. Ingaqhubeka futhi nasempilweni yakho. UJesu ufuna ukukukhombisa uthando Iwakhe futhi akwenze kuphumelele ukuba wazi uBaba wakhe uNkulukulu. Ukwenza lokhu ngendlela efanayo nanamuhla nendlela enza ngayo kubalandeli bakhe bokuqala : uzothumela uMoya wakhe oNgcwele ukuba ahlale kuwe ukuze ashintshe impilo yakho ngaphakathi nangaphandle. Okwakumnyama kuzoba-mhlophe, okwakuzogcina ekufeni manje kuzobheka empilweni yangaphakathi. Bonga uJesu, ukuba inhloso kaNkulunkulu ngempilo yakho igcwaliseke.
 